Enterprise-based CTMS solutions cater to larger organizations with multiple research sites, offering centralized control over clinical trials. These systems enable streamlined management and coordination across various locations, ensuring consistency and efficiency in trial operations. On the other hand, site-based CTMS solutions are more tailored for individual research sites or smaller organizations, providing localized control and customization to address specific trial requirements.

